WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.650 --> 00:00:01.650
Best Breed Ever!

00:00:01.650 --> 00:00:02.650
Cavalier King Charles Spaniels!

00:00:02.650 --> 00:00:03.650
Cavaliers came from the spaniel line, originating
in 1600s England.

00:00:03.650 --> 00:00:04.650
Cavaliers were once used as lap and feet warmers
for royalty.

00:00:04.650 --> 00:00:05.650
Cavaliers were also used for attracting fleas
from their owners' bodies.

00:00:05.650 --> 00:00:06.650
After WWII, only 6 Cavaliers survived.

00:00:06.650 --> 00:00:07.650
All modern Cavaliers can be traced to those
6.

00:00:07.650 --> 00:00:08.650
Cavalier King Charles Spaniel are different
from the King Charles Spaniel (aka the English

00:00:08.650 --> 00:00:09.650
Toy Spaniel) mainly by muzzle length.

00:00:09.650 --> 00:00:10.650
Sweet, gentle, and playful, Cavaliers are
known as the "Love Sponges" of dogs.

00:00:10.650 --> 00:00:11.650
Cavaliers are strictly indoor dogs, but they
still need their daily exercise.

00:00:11.650 --> 00:00:12.650
Cavaliers are friendly with other dogs, pets,
kids, adults, grandparents, and strangers.

00:00:12.650 --> 00:00:13.650
Cavaliers come in 4 color varieties.

00:00:13.650 --> 00:02:48.870
Cavaliers live to be 9 - 14 years old (63
to 84 in dog years).

